OL,3,CExperts call for action on 'nurse'
OL,4,Ctitle after death of Steve Bruce's
OL,5,Cgrandson
OL,7,FThe death of the four-month-old
OL,8,Fgrandson of football manager Steve
OL,9,FBruce is a "tragic reminder" of the
OL,10,F"urgent need to protect the title of
OL,11,Fnurse", experts have said.
OL,13,FIt comes after a coroner at Stockport
OL,14,FCoroner's Court criticised the
OL,15,F"misleading" use of the title
OL,16,F"maternity nurse" after the death of
OL,17,FMadison Bruce Smith.
OL,26,@qD@LOUqD@\O]rD@AOUsD@FO]wD@AOUwD@LO]xD@
OL,26,AAOUxD@QO]
