PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775639132
OL,3,CExperts call for action on 'nurse'
OL,4,Ctitle after death of Steve Bruce's
OL,5,Cgrandson
OL,7,FMadison was found unresponsive by his
OL,8,Ffather, ex-Leeds United and Fulham
OL,9,Fstriker Matt Smith, on the morning of
OL,10,F18 October 2024.
OL,12,FThe infant could not be resuscitated
OL,13,Fat the family home in Trafford and was
OL,14,Ftaken to Wythenshawe Hospital, where
OL,15,Fhe was pronounced dead.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775639132
OL,3,CExperts call for action on 'nurse'
OL,4,Ctitle after death of Steve Bruce's
OL,5,Cgrandson
OL,7,FMr Smith and his wife, Bruce's
OL,8,Fdaughter Amy, had employed a maternity
OL,9,Fnurse through a company named Ruthie
OL,10,FMaternity Services after their son had
OL,11,Fdifficulties sleeping in the
OL,12,Fafternoons.
OL,14,FThe maternity nurse - who had no
OL,15,Fmedical qualifications other than
OL,16,Fbasic first aid - suggested Madison
OL,17,Fshould be positioned to sleep on his
OL,18,Ffront to help sleep, also known as the
OL,19,Fprone position.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775639132
OL,3,CExperts call for action on 'nurse'
OL,4,Ctitle after death of Steve Bruce's
OL,5,Cgrandson
OL,7,FThis is despite advice that babies
OL,8,Fshould always be placed on their back
OL,9,Fto sleep.
OL,11,FA post-mortem examination was unable
OL,12,Fto give a cause of death but it was
OL,13,Fidentified that prone sleeping created
OL,14,Fan increased risk of his sudden
OL,15,Funexpected death.
OL,17,FFormer Manchester United player Bruce
OL,18,Fwas managing Blackpool FC at the time
OL,19,Fof the incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775639132
OL,3,CExperts call for action on 'nurse'
OL,4,Ctitle after death of Steve Bruce's
OL,5,Cgrandson
OL,7,FIn a message posted on the club's
OL,8,Fofficial X account, he said: "It's
OL,9,Fbeen the worst time of my family's
OL,10,Fentire lives and is something no
OL,11,Ffamily should have to endure."
OL,13,FWriting a prevention of future deaths
OL,14,Freport, Alison Mutch, Senior Coroner
OL,15,Ffor Manchester South, said: "Any
OL,16,Fperson can describe themselves as a
OL,17,Fmaternity nurse or a sleep nurse or a
OL,18,Fpost-natal nurse.
OL,26,@pD@^OUsD@^O]wD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775639132
OL,3,CExperts call for action on 'nurse'
OL,4,Ctitle after death of Steve Bruce's
OL,5,Cgrandson
OL,7,F"No qualifications are required and
OL,8,Fthere is no regulation of persons
OL,9,Fholding themselves out as maternity
OL,10,Fnurses or the agencies that offer
OL,11,Ftraining courses or their services.
OL,13,F"In this case, the maternity nurse and
OL,14,Fthe owner of the agency had no medical
OL,15,Fqualifications other than a basic
OL,16,Ffirst aid qualification.
OL,18,F"The use of the word nurse gave the
OL,19,Fimpression of a level of knowledge and
OL,20,Fskills that were not present."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775639132
OL,3,CExperts call for action on 'nurse'
OL,4,Ctitle after death of Steve Bruce's
OL,5,Cgrandson
OL,7,FShe called on the Department of Health
OL,8,Fand Social Care to act, adding:
OL,9,F"Anyone, the inquest was told, can
OL,10,Fattach the term 'nurse' to a word such
OL,11,Fas night/maternity/post-natal.
OL,13,F"The inquest was told that only the
OL,14,Fterm 'registered nurse' is protected
OL,15,Fand restricted in its use.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775639132
OL,3,CExperts call for action on 'nurse'
OL,4,Ctitle after death of Steve Bruce's
OL,5,Cgrandson
OL,7,F"An individual who has no medical
OL,8,Ftraining or formal early years
OL,9,Ftraining can offer their services to a
OL,10,Ffamily with young children describing
OL,11,Fthemselves as, for example, a
OL,12,Fmaternity nurse.
OL,14,F"This can, the inquest was told, give
OL,15,Fa misleading impression of their
OL,16,Fexpertise and skill set to a family
OL,17,Femploying them.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775639132
OL,3,CExperts call for action on 'nurse'
OL,4,Ctitle after death of Steve Bruce's
OL,5,Cgrandson
OL,7,F"A statutory bar on the word nurse
OL,8,Fbeing used by anyone other than a
OL,9,Fregistered nurse on the NMC (Nursing
OL,10,Fand Midwifery Council) register would
OL,11,Favoid this situation from arising."
OL,13,FMs Mutch also urged officials to
OL,14,Fpromote safe sleeping habits.
OL,16,FCommenting on the prevention of future
OL,17,Fdeaths report, a Royal College of
OL,18,FNursing spokesperson said: "This is
OL,19,Fthe tragic reminder of the urgent need
OL,20,Fto protect the title of nurse.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@cO]zD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775639132
OL,3,CExperts call for action on 'nurse'
OL,4,Ctitle after death of Steve Bruce's
OL,5,Cgrandson
OL,7,F"Patients and their families deserve
OL,8,Fto know that when they are being
OL,9,Ftreated by a nurse they can trust the
OL,10,Fknowledge, professionalism and
OL,11,Fclinical expertise that brings.
OL,13,F"Nursing is a highly-skilled, safety-
OL,14,Fcritical profession and we must now
OL,15,Fsee urgent action from government to
OL,16,Fprevent those without the right
OL,17,Fqualifications from calling themselves
OL,18,Fa nurse."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
